<li id="cite_note-20"><b><a href="#cite_ref-20" title="">^</a></b> U.S. Geological Survey, <a href="http://minerals.usgs.gov/minerals/pubs/commodity/niobium/tantamcs05.pdf" class="external text" title="http://minerals.usgs.gov/minerals/pubs/commodity/niobium/tantamcs05.pdf" rel="nofollow">Mineral Commodity Summaries, January 2005</a>, Tantalum p. 166-7</li>
